<div class="tc">
<p><b><h4>PRICES:</h4></b></p>
<p>The "Min" or "<b>Less than Full Case Price</b>" applies to items that are purchased in quantities that are less than the full master carton, where listed.<br>The "Case" or "<b>Full Case Price</b>" applies to full master carton purchases.</p>
<div class="tc2">
<p><b><i>For Special Markets / Decorator customers:</i></b></p>
</div>
<p>The "<b>$1,000 Entry Price</b>" applies to those listed items when the total order exceeds $1,000 and the order quantity must be equal to or greater than multiples of Inner Pack or Case quantity.  Any combination of product will contribute to the $1,000 total.
<br><br>The "Pallet Quantity Price" applies to those listed glassware items when purchased in full pallet quantities. Quantities purchased below full pallet quantities will be invoiced at the "List Price" or at the "$1,000 Entry Price", depending on the value of the order.</p>
<div class="tc2">
<p><b><i>For Gift / Retail Store customers:</i></b></p>
</div>
<p>The "<b>$100 Special Case / Promo Price</b>" applies to those listed items when the <u>total order</u> exceeds $100 and the order quantity must be equal to or greater than multiples of Inner Pack or Case quantity.  Any combination of product will contribute to the $100 total.
<br><br>Prices and availability are subject to change without prior notice. </p>
</div>

