<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 vert ">
<div class="tc">
<p><b><h4>SHIPPING LEAD TIME:</h4></b></p>
<p>Our typical lead time to ship in-stock, credit-approved orders under pallet quantities is 1 to 3 business days.
<br><br>No changes may be made to the order once it is in the warehouse. If a change or cancellation is required after the order has been prepared for shipping, a $25 processing fee will apply.</p>
</div>

<div class="tc">
<p><b><h4>ADD-ONS:</h4></b></p>
<p>Add-ons to an existing order already in house will be accepted, but once initiated; the order may lose its position in the shipping queue. Once an order ships, an 'add-on' is considered a new order and subject to normal terms.</p>
</div>


<div class="tc">
<p><b><h4>DAMAGE & LOSS CLAIMS:</h4></b></p>
<p>Please note that all common carrier shipments are forwarded at a release value not exceeding $.90 per pound unless you request, in writing, to ship at a higher release value or at actual value. The $.90 release value will <b>NOT</b> insure the full value of the product if loss or damage occurs while in transit and, hence, the consignee will bear all responsibility for the loss or damage.
<br><br>
All orders are shipped FOB Shipping Point and all carrier loss or damage claims are <u>your</u> responsibility.</p>
</div>


<div class="tc">
<p><b><h4>BACK ORDERS:</h4></b></p>
<p>In your best interest, the decision concerning back orders must be yours. For your own protection against excessive freight costs, we will automatically cancel all back orders under $50.00 in value, unless you specify otherwise. For back orders over $50.00, we will forward a letter indicating the items that have not shipped. If signed and returned, this letter will activate your back order, which will ship when merchandise becomes available. </p>
</div>

<div class="tc">
<p><b><h4>RETURNS:</h4></b></p>
<p>Returns will not be accepted without prior written or verbal authorization. No exceptions will be made to this condition. Credit will not be issued for unauthorized returns or refused shipments. We will not accept responsibility for any charges resulting from unauthorized return.</p>
